{"tid":359353,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先去左M記食野,聽到有人話香港寬頻同有線係一樣","createTime":"2017-08-14T12:20:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T12:20:29.000Z","uid":122823,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3fcafec7089bbed98b05b9d1daba38be25c7fee2","tid":359353,"uid":122823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T12:20:29.000Z","msg":"個阿婆就約左個寬頻仔係M記等啦,寬頻仔就話香港寬頻同有線係一樣嫁,都係光纖上網,聽到阿婆既聲線好想喊咁款,寬頻仔就起勢咁話我有職員証,唔會呃你既,你簽左先,唔啱都可以唔要嫁嘛,最後阿婆都簽左<br />\n<br />\n聽到個阿婆話用開網上含,乜香港寬頻好過網上含咩?定係錢作怪呢?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">怪唔得咁多癈老話比人呃錢啦</span></span>,自己唔識就搵D後生攪嘛,又要懶醒自己去簽約<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/593211/%E3%80%90%E7%9C%9F%E4%BA%BA%E7%9C%9F%E4%BA%8B%E3%80%91CUT%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E8%8B%A6%E6%88%B03%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E3%80%80%E7%B5%82%E6%96%BC%E5%BE%97%E5%92%97%EF%BC%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F593211%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%259C%259F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%259C%259F%25E4%25BA%258B%25E3%2580%2591CUT%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B7%259A%25E8%258B%25A6%25E6%2588%25B03%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E3%2580%2580%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%2596%25BC%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%2592%2597%25EF%25BC%2581&d=XgYSpDQkWPfYcZ3%2BIBN8pCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=2542abae\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/593211/%E3%80%90%E7%9C%9F%E4%BA%BA%E7%9C%9F%E4%BA%8B%E3%80%91CUT%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E8%8B%A6%E6%88%B03%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E3%80%80%E7%B5%82%E6%96%BC%E5%BE%97%E5%92%97%EF%BC%81</a><br />\n有線好似係易請難送,香港寬頻我就唔多清楚"}]}